data.description: A completely remodeled 2 Story, 5bed, 2.5 Bath with a bonus large loft upstairs and master bedroom on the first floor, in Newport Isles, one of the nicest communities in Port Saint Lucie. This home is perfect for large families. The house is Turnkey condition and features an open floor plan with new tile throughout the entire house, remodeled kitchen and bathrooms. A huge yard backing up to private preserve with plenty of room for a private pool. Gated Community with 3 pools includes Kiddy pool, fitness Center, Basketball, Tennis, Volleyball Cts, Barbecue Area. The Community Offers Resort Style amenities including a beautiful club house. and tons of activities for everyone. Located in a great location with easy Access to I-95 and Turnpike and in a great School Zone. Hurry! IT won't last!
